  Drop upstreamed patch.

*mc-4.8.10 (03 Aug 2013)

  03 Aug 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.10.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  15 Jul 2013; Alex Alexander <wired@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.9.ebuild,
  +files/mc-4.8.9-ncurses-include-fix.patch:
  fixed ncurses detection, bug #476932

*mc-4.8.9 (12 Jul 2013)

  12 Jul 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.9.ebuild,
  mc-9999.ebuild:
  Version bump. With unlimited file sizes during edition!

*mc-4.8.8-r2 (09 Jul 2013)

  09 Jul 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org> -mc-4.8.1-r1.ebuild,
  -mc-4.8.8.ebuild, +mc-4.8.8-r2.ebuild, mc-9999.ebuild,
  -files/mc-4.8.1-fix-vfs-test.patch, -files/mc-4.8.1-muldefs.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.1-muldefs-in.patch,
  +files/mc-4.8.8-race_cond_create_tmp_dir.patch,
  +files/mc-4.8.8-wrong_char_in_menu_file.patch:
  Revision bump to fix bug #403863 and bug #461284. Fixed unquoted variable in
  live ebuild. Removed old versions.

  03 Jul 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org>
  +files/mc-4.8.9-unknown-opts.patch, mc-9999.ebuild:
  Added check for unknown ./configure options. Followed upstream in '--with-
  edit' to '--with-internal-edit' renaming.

*mc-4.8.8-r1 (19 Jun 2013)

  19 Jun 2013; Alex Alexander <wired@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.8-r1.ebuild,
  +files/mc-4.8.8-segfault-unowned-temp-dir.patch:
  patch for bug #473244

*mc-4.8.8 (03 Apr 2013)

  03 Apr 2013; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.8.ebuild:
  Version bump.

  13 Jan 2013; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  s390/sh stable wrt #436518

*mc-4.8.7-r1 (11 Jan 2013)

  11 Jan 2013; Lars Wendler <polynomial-c@gentoo.org>
  -files/mc-4.8.1-fix-fallocate-xBSD.patch, -mc-4.8.3-r2.ebuild,
  -files/mc-4.8.3-fix-chown-crash.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.3-fix-relative-symlink-creation-crash.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.3-missing-do_panel_cd_stub_env.c, -mc-4.8.4-r3.ebuild,
  -files/mc-4.8.4-Ticket-2851-fixes-of-ext.d-scripts.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.4-Ticket-2853-fileposition-in-mcedit.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.4-Ticket-2856-aspell-sigsegv.patch,
  -files/mc-4.8.4-Ticket-2858-htmlview-segfault.patch, -mc-4.8.6.ebuild,
  +mc-4.8.7-r1.ebuild, metadata.xml:
  Fixed handling of external programs with xdg USE flag being unset (bug
  #449936). Removed old versions. Added myself as maintainer.

  07 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for alpha, wrt bug #436518

  06 Jan 2013; Markus Meier <maekke@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  arm stable, bug #436518

  05 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for sparc, wrt bug #436518

  04 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for ia64, wrt bug #436518

  04 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc64, wrt bug #436518

  04 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for ppc, wrt bug #436518

  02 Jan 2013; Agostino Sarubbo <ago@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.7.ebuild:
  Stable for amd64, wrt bug #436518

