*mc-4.8.0-r2 (30 Nov 2011)

  30 Nov 2011; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.0-r2.ebuild,
  +files/mc-4.8.0-fix-ftp-spaces.patch:
  Fix annoying leading spaces in ftp directories (upstream patch)

  11 Nov 2011; Naohiro Aota <naota@gentoo.org> mc-4.7.5.3.ebuild,
  mc-4.7.5.5.ebuild, mc-4.8.0.ebuild, mc-4.8.0-r1.ebuild:
  Apply Bug #376943 fix to all related ebuilds

