  Install cons.saver only on Linux. Bug #376943

*mc-4.8.0-r1 (01 Nov 2011)

  01 Nov 2011; Alex Alexander <wired@gentoo.org> +mc-4.8.0-r1.ebuild,
  metadata.xml:
  new use flag: mclib. install NEWS file, bug 389143

