  Added myself to maintainers.

  21 Oct 2011; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> mc-4.8.0.ebuild,
  +files/mc-4.8.0-fix-nls.patch:
  Fixed build failure in USE=-nls case by Nikos Chantziaras (bug #387949)

*mc-4.8.0 (20 Oct 2011)
*mc-4.7.5.5 (20 Oct 2011)

  20 Oct 2011; Sergei Trofimovich <slyfox@gentoo.org> +mc-4.7.5.5.ebuild,
  +mc-4.8.0.ebuild:
  Version bump (requested by Anton Kochkov in bug #387883)

  14 Aug 2011; Fabian Groffen <grobian@gentoo.org> mc-4.7.5.3.ebuild:
  Allow linkage to succeed on Solaris, bug #378699 by Daniel Vergien

  07 Aug 2011; Raúl Porcel <armin76@gentoo.org> mc-4.7.5.2.ebuild:
  alpha/ia64/s390/sh/sparc stable wrt #373225

